  "description": "Industrial archaeology at 800 meters. A compartment inside a sunken freighter — the allpass diffusion creates the specific acoustic signature of hollow steel rooms filled with water. bodyChar=2, bodyFeedback=0.5. filterCutoff=180: very dark, the wreck has been down a long time.",
